  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nWhen debugging a Solidity contract in Hardhat test environment, it's convenient to use `hardhat/console.sol`. Unfortunately when running tests on Optimism client, nothing is printed.\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nI'd like to have `hardhat/console.sol` working like on Hardhat or an equivalent tool.\r\n\r\n**Describe alternatives you've considered**\r\nAdd a different debugging tool, which would be just as useful?\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\nNone.\r\n",
