    "body": "I see two options for doing this:\r\n1. Capture these logs in the EVM inside Geth and print them out in the Geth logs. Users would have to do something along the lines of `docker-compose logs l2geth | grep \"hardhat:\".\r\n2. Capture the logs and attach them to the receipt, then modify the `hardhat-ovm` plugin to print out the logs. That could be pretty cool but not sure how easy that is.",
